<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>This class is used to render <db:code>wl_shell</db:code>, <db:code>xdg_shell</db:code> or <db:code>ivi_application</db:code> surfaces as part of a Qt Quick scene. It handles moving and resizing triggered by clicking on the window decorations.</db:para>
